        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This black pearl sparkles with light. The resonant power allows you to cast <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Sending]{Sending}</em> once per day.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">R</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> you are targeted by a mental effect</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You receive a +4 status bonus to your saving throw against the triggering effect.</p>\n<p>Whether or not your save is successful, the aeon stone attempts a counteract check at [[/r {1d20+30} #Counteract]]{1d20+30]] to immediately reflect a copy of the effect back at the originator, targeting it using the creature's own relevant statistics but controlling the effect as if you had cast it.</p>\n<p>Every time you activate this aeon stone, attempt a DC 5 flat check. On a failure, the stone shatters and loses its magical properties forever.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.equipment-effects.Effect: Aeon Stone (Black Pearl)]{Effect: Aeon Stone (Black Pearl)}</p>"
